x+1\mid x^n+1
2^n+1
n=2^u
x^n=(x+1-1)^n=(-1)^n=  -1\mod x+1
\begin{align}   \frac{{{x^n} + 1}}{{x + 1}} &= \frac{{{{( - x)}^n} - 1}}{{( - x) - 1}} \cr     &= \frac{{{u^n} - 1}}{{u - 1}} \cr     &= 1 + u + {u^2} +  \cdots  + {u^{n - 1}} \cr     &= 1 - x + {x^2} -  +  \cdots  + {\left( { - 1} \right)^{n - 1}}{x^{n - 1}} \end{align} 
